  <article class="content-page">
    <h1>About Wenji</h1>

    <p>I’m Wenji, a Stardew Valley mod creator. I make the content I want to play but can’t find in the game yet.</p>

    <p>
      I started making mods in 2025 and went from running a small toolbox site to becoming a full-time mod developer.
      My work starts with gameplay ideas first: I ask “what would make this game more fun?”, then build it into something playable.
    </p>

    <h2>Creative approach</h2>
    <p>
      I don’t focus on simple stat edits or skin replacements. I want mods that change the way you play —
      starting from scratch on Ginger Island, or using a flute as a real gameplay system instead of a menu button.
      If I don’t enjoy playing it myself, I won’t release it.
    </p>

    <h2>What comes next</h2>
    <p>
      I’ll keep building Stardew Valley mods, especially the larger Ginger Island Survival expansion and new systems like Starfall Flute.
      I’m also interested in modding games such as <strong>Don’t Starve</strong>, while working toward making my own indie game.
    </p>

    <h2>Where to find my work</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/profile/IamWENJI/mods?gameId=1303" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nexus Mods</a> — all released mod downloads</li>
